# Atlas Broker Credentials
# ==============================
#
# DO NOT put real credentials in this file.
# DO NOT copy this to .env in the repo directory.
#
# Instead, use ONE of these secure methods:
#
# Option 1 (recommended): Secrets file in your home directory
#   Run: atlas setup-secrets
#   This creates ~/.atlas-secrets.json with chmod 600
#
# Option 2: Environment variables
#   export MOOMOO_TRADE_PWD='your-6-digit-pin'
#
# The secrets file is NEVER inside the git repo.
